'''費爾干納龍屬'''（[[屬|屬]]名：{{lang|la|''Ferganasaurus''}}，意為「[[費爾干納盆地|費爾干納]]的蜥蜴」）是分類地位不明確<ref name = Pol2011>{{Cite journal | authors = Pol, D.; Garrido, A.; Cerda, I. A. | year = 2011 | title = A New Sauropodomorph Dinosaur from the Early Jurassic of Patagonia and the Origin and Evolution of the Sauropod-type Sacrum | journal = ''[[PLoS_ONE|PLoS ONE]]'' | volume = 6 | issue = 1 | issn = 1932-6203 | pages = e14572 | pmc = 3027623 | pmid = 21298087 | doi = 10.1371/journal.pone.0014572 | url = https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0014572 | access-date = 2021-05-18 | archive-date = 2021-05-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210502200825/https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371%2Fjournal.pone.0014572 | dead-url = no }}</ref>的中大型[[蜥腳類|蜥腳類]][[恐龍|恐龍]]<ref name = Holtz>{{cite book | author = Holtz, T. R. Jr. | chapter = Dinosaur Genus List [Updated 13 January 2011] | title = ''Dinosaurs: The Most Complete, Up-to-Date Encyclopedia for Dinosaur Lovers of All Ages'' | publisher = Indiana University Press | isbn = 0-375-82419-7 | year = 2012 | chapter-url = http://www.geol.umd.edu/~tholtz/dinoappendix/HoltzappendixWinter2011.pdf | access-date = 2018-07-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170812011954/http://www.geol.umd.edu/~tholtz/dinoappendix/HoltzappendixWinter2011.pdf | archive-date = 2017-08-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name = Paul2016>{{ cite book | author = Paul, G. S. | title = ''The Princeton Field Guide to Dinosaurs: Second Edition'' | publisher = Princeton University Press | isbn = 978-0-691-16766-4 | year = 2016 | page = 200 }}</ref><ref name = Molina-Pérez>{{ cite book | author = Molina-Pérez, R.; Larramendi, A. | others = (譯) Donaghey, J. | title = 
''Dinosaur Facts and Figures: The Sauropods and Other Sauropodomorphs'' | publisher = [[Princeton_University_Press|Princeton University Press]] | year = 2020 | isbn = 978-0-691-19069-3 }}</ref>，生存於[[侏羅紀|中侏羅世]]的[[卡洛夫期|卡洛夫期]]<ref name = Alifanov2003>{{ Cite journal | authors = Alifanov, V. R.; Averianov, A. O. | year = 2003 | title = ''Ferganasaurus verzilini'', gen. et sp. nov., a new neosauropod (Dinosauria, Saurischia, Sauropoda) from the Middle Jurassic of Fergana Valley, Kirghizia | journal = ''Journal of Vertebrate Paleontology'' | volume = 23 | issue = 2 | issn = 0272-4634 | pages = 358-372 | doi = 10.1671/0272-4634(2003)023[0358:FVGESN]2.0.CO;2 | url = }}</ref><ref name = Alifanov2008>{{ Cite journal | authors = Alifanov, V. R.; Martin, T.; Skutschas, P. P.; Rezvyi, A. S.; Bakirov, A. A. | year = 2008 | title = Amphibians from the Middle Jurassic Balabansai Svita in the Fergana Depression, Kyrgyzstan (Central Asia) | journal = ''Palaeontology'' | volume = 51 | issue = 2 | issn = 0031-0239 | pages = 471-485 | doi = 10.1111/j.1475-4983.2007.00748.x | url = }}</ref>。已被確認的化石僅有部分屬於四肢和軀體後部的骨骼，為1960年代從現今[[吉爾吉斯|吉爾吉斯]]西部的[[塔什庫梅爾|塔什庫梅爾]]附近所發現，屬於{{le|巴拉班塞層|Balabansai Formation}}<ref name = Alifanov2003/>，在當時是[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]境內出土的第一種蜥腳類化石<ref name = Rhozdestvensky>{{ cite book | author = Рождественский, А. К. | chapter = Среднеазиатские динозавры | title = 
''На поиски динозавров в Гоби'' | publisher = Наука | year = 1969 | isbn = | pages = 240-259 | language = ru }}</ref>。

費爾干納龍的名稱早在化石發現後的第三年便被提出，然而直到2003年才被正式描述並發表，是維持[[無資格名稱|無資格]]狀態最久的{{le|有效學名|Valid name (zoology)|有效}}蜥腳類學名<ref name = Molina-Pérez/>。由於缺少大部分骨骼導致可供比對的特徵有限，不易釐清其確切的分類歸屬，但迄今的[[譜系學|譜系]]分析仍都確認了費爾干納龍屬於[[真蜥腳類|真蜥腳類]]，其中有些研究視其為真蜥腳類的[[基群|基幹成員]]<ref name = Holtz/><ref name = Ksepka2010>{{cite journal | author = Ksepka, D. T.; Norell, M. A. | year = 2010 | title = The Illusory Evidence for Asian Brachiosauridae: New Material of ''Erketu ellisoni'' and a Phylogenetic Reappraisal of Basal Titanosauriformes | journal = ''American Museum Novitates'' | volume = 3700 | issn = 0003-0082 | pages = 1-27 | doi = 10.1206/3700.2 | url = http://digitallibrary.amnh.org/handle/2246/6087 | access-date = 2021-03-19 | archive-date = 2020-09-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200918205430/http://digitallibrary.amnh.org/handle/2246/6087 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name = Holwerda2019>{{cite journal | author = Holwerda, F. M.; Evans, M.; Liston, J. J. | year = 2019 | title = Additional sauropod dinosaur material from the Callovian Oxford Clay Formation, Peterborough, UK: evidence for higher sauropod diversity | journal = ''PeerJ'' | volume = 7 | issn = 2376-5992 | pages = e6404 | doi = 10.7717/peerj.6404 | url = https://peerj.com/articles/6404/ | access-date = 2021-05-05 | archive-date = 2021-05-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210506205841/https://peerj.com/articles/6404/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>，也有觀點認為其屬於真蜥腳類中更衍化的[[新蜥腳類|新蜥腳類]]<ref name = Molina-Pérez/>{{rp|31, 253}}<ref name = Alifanov2003/>{{rp|360}}。

