== 古生態學 ==
埋藏正模標本的層位形成於[[中侏羅世|中侏羅世]]的[[卡洛夫期|卡洛夫期]]，屬於{{le|巴拉班塞層|Balabansai Formation}}的一部分<ref name = Alifanov2003/>{{rp|360}}<ref name = Nesov1995/>{{rp|82}}。巴拉班塞層的[[地質年代|年代]]約介於[[中侏羅世|中侏羅世]]的[[巴通期|巴通期]]後期<ref name = Alifanov2008/>{{rp|471}}至[[晚侏羅世|晚侏羅世]]的[[牛津期|牛津期]]後期<ref name = DePelsmaeker2018>{{cite journal | author = De Pelsmaeker, E.; Jolivet, M.; Laborde, A.; Poujol, M.; Robin, C.; Zhimulev, F. I.; Nachtergaele, S.; Glorie, S.; De Clercq, S.; Batalev, V. Y.; De Grave, J. | year = 2018 | title = Source-to-sink dynamics in the Kyrgyz Tien Shan from the Jurassic to the Paleogene: Insights from sedimentological and detrital zircon U-Pb analyses | journal = ''Gondwana Research'' | volume = 54 | issn = 1342-937X | pages = 180-204 | doi = 10.1016/j.gr.2017.09.004 | url = https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1342937X17300679 }}</ref>{{rp|185-187}}之間，岩石組成的改變情形顯示，此時的費爾干納地勢正逐漸[[地層下陷|下陷]]，且由淺水湖泊過渡至瀕臨[[特提斯洋|特提斯洋]]的沿海環境<ref name = DePelsmaeker2018/><ref name = Morin2021>{{cite journal | author = Morin, J.; Jolivet, M.; Shaw, D.; Bourquin, S.; Bataleva, E. | year = 2021 | title = New sedimentological and palynological data from the Yarkand-Fergana Basin (Kyrgyz Tian Shan): Insights on its Mesozoic paleogeographic and tectonic evolution | journal = ''Geoscience Frontiers'' | volume = 12 | issue = 1 | issn = 1674-9871 | pages = 183-202 | doi = 10.1016/j.gsf.2020.04.010 | url = https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1674987120301122 | access-date = 2021-06-15 | archive-date = 2022-02-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220207041152/https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1674987120301122 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。正模標本所在地層的沉積物主要是[[黏土|黏土]]或[[粒徑|粒徑]]排序分明的[[砂岩|砂岩]]，應與河流[[搬運作用|搬運作用]]有關，而[[古水流|古水流]]也顯示該地當時有大河向西流經，沿著大致平行於現今[[納倫河|納倫河]]的河道注入特提斯洋<ref name = Averianov2005/>{{rp|137, 138}}<ref name = DePelsmaeker2018/>。巴拉班塞層已知的[[動物相|動物相]]包含[[鳥腳類|鳥腳類]]（[[費爾干納頭龍|費爾干納頭龍]]<ref name = Averianov2005/>與「[[非正式命名恐龍列表#费尔干纳剑龙|費爾干納劍龍]]」<ref name = AverianovEtAl2007>{{cite journal | author = Averianov, A. O.; Bakirov, A. A.; Martin, T. | year = 2007 | title = First definitive stegosaur from the Middle Jurassic of Kyrgyzstan | journal = ''Paläontologische Zeitschrift'' | volume = 81 | issn = 0031-0220 | pages = 440-446 | doi = 10.1007/BF02990255 | url = https://www.researchgate.net/publication/225997295_First_definitive_stegosaur_from_the_Middle_Jurassic_of_Kyrgyzstan | access-date = 2021-07-03 | archive-date = 2021-03-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210326214525/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/225997295_First_definitive_stegosaur_from_the_Middle_Jurassic_of_Kyrgyzstan | dead-url = no }}</ref>）與[[獸腳類|獸腳類]]恐龍、[[哺乳類|哺乳類]]<ref name = Martin2010>{{cite journal | author = Martin, T.; Averianov, A. O. | year = 2010 | title = Mammals from the Middle Jurassic Balabansai Formation of the Fergana Depression, Kyrgyzstan | journal = ''Journal of Vertebrate Paleontology'' | volume = 30 | issue = 3 | issn = 0272-4634 | pages = 855-871 | doi = 10.1080/02724631003758045 | url = https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/Mammals-from-the-Middle-Jurassic-Balabansai-of-the-Martin-Averianov/1c99cea9cff85a1444d189f08fce59ac9606d42c | access-date = 2021-06-07 | archive-date = 2021-06-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210615004314/https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/Mammals-from-the-Middle-Jurassic-Balabansai-of-the-Martin-Averianov/1c99cea9cff85a1444d189f08fce59ac9606d42c | dead-url = no }}</ref>、[[兩生類|兩生類]]、[[翼龍|翼龍]]、[[龜鱉目|龜鱉類]]（{{le|新疆龜屬|Xinjiangchelys|新疆龜}}<ref name = Nessov1995b>{{cite journal | author = Nessov, L. A. | year = 1995 | title = On Some Mesozoic Turtles of the Fergana Depression (Kyrgyzstan) and Dzhungar Alatau Ridge (Kazakhstan) | journal = ''Russian Journal of Herpetology'' | volume = 2 | issue = 2 | issn = 1026-2296 | pages = 134-141 | doi = 10.30906/1026-2296-1995-2-2-134-141 | url = }}</ref>），以及水生動物如[[蚌科|蚌]]<ref name = Kuzichkina>{{cite book | language = ru | last = Кузичкина | first = Ю. М. | chapter = Балабансайская Свита | editor = Министерство геологии СССР | script-title = ru:Стратиграфический словарь СССР: Триас, Юра, Мелсборник | trans-title = ''Stratigraphic Dictionary of the USSR: Triassic, Jurassic, Cretaceous'' | publisher = Недра | year = 1979 | page = 49 | url = https://www.geokniga.org/bookfiles/geokniga-1979stratigraficheskijslovartriasjuramel.pdf | title =  | access-date = 2021-07-03 | archive-date = 2021-07-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210708224711/https://www.geokniga.org/bookfiles/geokniga-1979stratigraficheskijslovartriasjuramel.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>、[[鱷類|鱷類]]（{{le|孫氏鱷屬|Sunosuchus|孫氏鱷}}<ref name = Averianov2001>{{cite journal | author = Averianov, A. O. | year = 2001 | title = ''Sunosuchus'' sp. (Crocodylomorpha, Goniopholididae) from the Middle Jurassic of Kirghisia | journal = ''Journal of Vertebrate Paleontology'' | volume = 20 | issue = 4 | issn = 0272-4634 | pages = 776-779 | doi = 10.1671/0272-4634(2000)020[0776:SSCGFT]2.0.CO;2 | url = https://www.researchgate.net/publication/232674702_Sunosuchus_sp_Crocodylomorpha_Goniopholididae_from_the_Middle_Jurassic_of_Kirghisia | access-date = 2021-07-03 | archive-date = 2021-07-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210709182849/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/232674702_Sunosuchus_sp_Crocodylomorpha_Goniopholididae_from_the_Middle_Jurassic_of_Kirghisia | dead-url = no }}</ref>）、[[離龍類|離龍類]]、[[軟骨魚|軟骨魚]]和[[硬骨魚|硬骨魚]]，顯示該地層同時保留了{{le|陸域生態系統|Terrestrial ecosystem|陸域}}與[[水域生態系統|水域生態系]]<ref name = Alifanov2008/><ref name = Averianov2005/>。此外，形成年代與巴拉班塞層相仿，位於今日[[準噶爾盆地|準噶爾盆地]]的{{le|齊古層|Qigu Formation}}也有類似的[[脊椎動物|脊椎動物]]組成情形<ref name = Averianov2005/>。

雖然費爾干納龍生活於水陸交會的環境，但巴拉班塞層中的{{le|鈣質結核|Caliche}}與數公分厚的{{le|鈣質土|Calcareous#Calcareous_soils}}，都表明此地層經歷過[[成土作用#鈣化作用|鈣化作用]]，然而[[根跡|根跡]]{{noteTag|1=root trace，當小型[[草本植物|草本植物]]紮在土壤中的根腐爛後，空出的空間會被土壤中的礦物填滿，形成有如植物根系痕跡一般的圖案<ref name = Zhang2020>{{cite journal | author = Zhang, L.; Bao, Z.-D.; Zhang, C.-M.; Dou, L.-X.; Fu, P.; Zhao, J.-H.; Wang, W.-X.; Ji, Y. | year = 2020 | title = Paleosols in an outcrop of red beds from the Upper Cretaceous Yaojia Formation, southern Songliao Basin, Jilin Province, NE China | journal = ''Journal of Palaeogeography'' | volume = 9 | issn = 2095-3836 | pages = 20 | doi = 10.1186/s42501-020-00069-7 | url = https://journalofpalaeogeography.springeropen.com/articles/10.1186/s42501-020-00069-7 | access-date = 2021-07-03 | archive-date = 2021-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210711042954/https://journalofpalaeogeography.springeropen.com/articles/10.1186/s42501-020-00069-7 | dead-url = no }}</ref>{{rp|1}}，是一個地層曾有植物生長的間接證據。}}的存在卻又顯示巴拉班塞層並不是在極度乾燥的環境下形成。因此，費爾干納龍的生存環境較可能處於半乾旱的[[草原氣候|草原氣候]]<ref name = DePelsmaeker2018/>{{rp|185}}<ref name = Jolivet2018>{{cite journal | author = Jolivet, M.; Boulvais, P.; Barrier, L.; Robin, C.; Heilbronn, G.; Ledoyen, J.; Ventroux, Q.; Jia, Y.; Guo, Z.; Bataleva, E. A. | year = 2018 | title = Oxygen and Carbon Stable Isotope Composition of Cretaceous to Pliocene Calcareous Paleosols in the Tian Shan Region (Central Asia): Controlling Factors and Paleogeographic Implications | journal = ''Geosciences'' | volume = 8 | issue = 9 | issn = 2076-3263 | pages = 330 | doi = 10.3390/geosciences8090330 | url = https://www.mdpi.com/2076-3263/8/9/330/htm | access-date = 2021-07-03 | archive-date = 2021-07-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210709183622/https://www.mdpi.com/2076-3263/8/9/330/htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>{{rp|12}}。

